<plot>'I'm Afraid I am Hitler' renders the heartfelt story of a man trapped in two worlds. Adien (Bernhard Forcher) has confined himself to his home for over a year because he guards a secret- a secret so horrifying-that, if exposed, would set the entire world against him. Set in 1976, this psychological drama portrays the frightful journey of a lonely man, believing himself to be the most brutal leader history has ever seen, and his longing for redemption.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?254877</url></doc>
